公司节省资金——众所周知，它们是由利润驱动的——我们可能不得不习惯看到电视和电影海报以及营销材料，从奇怪的到噩梦般的燃料等等。 。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/amazon-freevee-adds-terrifying-ai- generated-men-to-12-angry-men-poster-120011551.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazon-freevee-adds-terrifying-ai-generated-men-to-12-angry-men-poster-120011551.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5a85ffce-ce6d-4fe8-977b-693ab8785ca5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mariella Moon]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:00:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1717748003</ingested><modified> 2024-06-07T08:13:28+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="878" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F0bdb7fc0-249b-11ef-b9ff-73a60d26219d&amp;resize=1400%2C878&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=023ed3fbb250d63c5c1d94e506180eb150eda268" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="878" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F0bdb7