escription type="html"><![CDATA[<p>苹果全球开发者大会将于周一拉开帷幕，按照惯例，苹果公司将推出一系列新产品。但是，尽管它很想保留它的惊喜，但已经有足够的泄密让我们了解舞台上将展示的内容。 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/wwdc-2024-what-we-expect-to-come-out-of-apples-keynote-and-how-to-watch-195802167.html"><ins>我们整理了一份详尽的列表，列出了您应该了解的所有内容，从 AI 技巧到新的 iOS 功能</ins></a>。虽然苹果刚刚推出了新的 iPad，但我们总是希望看到一些令人兴奋的新硬件得到上台表演。</p><p> — 丹·库珀</p><h3 id="jump-link-the-biggest-stories-you-might-have-missed">您可能错过的最重要的故事</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktoks-ai-efforts-reportedly-exploit-loopholes-to-use-premium-nvidia-chips-173432988.html"><ins>据报道，TikTok 的 AI 工作利用漏洞使用优质 NVIDIA 芯片</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/weber-slate-griddle-review-a-smash-burger-machine-with-clever-features-163023562.html"><ins>Weber Slate 煎锅评论：具有巧妙功能的粉碎汉堡机</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ftc-launches-an-antitrust-probe-into-microsofts-deal-with-inflection-ai-130038896.html"><ins>FTC 对微软与 Inflection AI 的交易启动反垄断调查</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-photography-gifts-for-dads-135953254.html"><ins>送给爸爸的最佳摄影礼物</ins></a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-cwa-forge-labor-neutrality-agreement-covering-all-zenimax-workers-212643324.html"><ins>微软与 CWA 签署涵盖所有 ZeniMax 员工的劳工中立协议</ins></a></p><p><em>​​您可以每天将这些报告直接发送到您的收件箱。</em><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>在这里订阅！</em></a></p><p></p><h2 id="jump-link-boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss"><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><ins>波音公司的 Starliner 克服了与国际空间站对接的最后一秒问题</ins></a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-phew">唷。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/23790600-24b1-11ef-9fff-83cf525d8699" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/23790600-24b1-11ef-9fff-83cf525d8699" style="height:348px;width:620px;" alt="星际客机的形象" data-uuid="bf51482f-2266-3dcf-b5a4-1f0498613a44"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">美国宇航局电视台</div></figure></a><p>星际客机已<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><ins>成功与国际空间站对接，但就像它的发射一样，连接也并非没有问题</ins></a>。推进器故障阻止了第一次尝试，但第二次成功了。星际客机的机组人员将在空间站度过接下来的八天，然后我们只希望安全返回地球。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/boeings-starliner-overcomes-last-second-problems-to-dock-with-the-iss-194801249.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a> </p><h2 id="jump-link-starship-survives-re-entry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test"> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><ins>星舰在第四次飞行测试成功后重返大气层并溅落在印度洋</ins></a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-more-milestones-for-the-heavy-vehicle">重型车辆的更多里程碑。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/4398e680-24b1-11ef-9776-cf88e5d0a91c" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/4398e680-24b1-11ef-9776-cf88e5d0a91c" style="height:328px;width:620px;" alt="星舰的图像" data-uuid="97d8a157-ac1f-3f64-a81c-e425b12d1225"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">太空探索技术公司</div></figure></a><p>SpaceX 巨大的 Starship 火箭在<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><ins>发射和重新进入大气层后跨越了几个里程碑，最后成功降落在印度洋</ins></a>。返程途中出现了一些问题，包括下降时襟翼开始烧毁。但在同时展示了如此多的能力后，SpaceX 的情绪可能会很胜利。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starship-survives-reentry-to-splash-down-in-the-indian-ocean-after-successful-fourth-flight-test-142912013.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a> </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2 id="jump-link-apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac"> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><ins>据报道，苹果将为 iPhone 和 Mac 开发专用的密码应用程序</ins></a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-are-1password-and-lastpass-at-risk-of-being-sherlocked">1Password 和 LastPass 是否有被 Sherlock 锁定的风险？</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p> WWDC 之前的最新传言是，苹果将为<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><ins>iOS 和 macOS 构建自己的密码管理器</ins></a>。该公司已经内置了一个复杂的密码管理器，但有传言称，独立的应用程序将更易于使用，也更有吸引力。如果属实，可能会引发人们的担忧，即 1Password 和 LastPass 等第三方密码管理器面临被挤出该领域的风险。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-what-to-expect-from-apples-big-event-111524145.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-what-to-expect-from-apples-big-event-111524145.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 90d9f2b1-2305-420e-a6b4-a9a2def8e5ec</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Daniel Cooper]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:15:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1717754134</ingested><modified> 202