gnature=7938329cd7cf9e19055e4a23eb995efb61bd4846" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Will Lipman Photography for Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The best laptops for gaming and schoolwork]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The best laptops for gaming and schoolwork]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple will reportedly build a dedicated Passwords app for the iPhone and Mac]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据<em>彭博社</em>的 Mark Gurman 周四<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/apple-to-debut-passwords-app-in-challenge-to-1password-lastpass?sref=10lNAhZ9" data-original-link="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/apple-to-debut-passwords-app-in-challenge-to-1password-lastpass?sref=10lNAhZ9">报道</a>，苹果计划在下一代 iPhone 和 Mac 操作系统中构建一个密码管理应用程序。这款新应用程序简称为“Passwords”，将与 1Password 和 LastPass 等现有密码管理器竞争，后者通常向人们收取每月生成和存储唯一密码的费用。苹果计划在 6 月 10 日举行的公司年度<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/wwdc-2024-how-to-watch-apples-keynote-on-june-10-153000518.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/wwdc-2024-how-to-watch-apples-keynote-on-june-10-153000518.html">全球开发者大会</a>上发布该应用程序。</p><p> Apple 已通过 iCloud 钥匙串生成并存储唯一密码，该功能可通过浏览器扩展在您拥有的所有 Apple 设备以及 Windows PC 之间同步密码。但奇怪的是，存储在 iCloud 钥匙串中的密码却存在于“设置”应用中，这使得查找或更改密码变得很麻烦。在苹果设备中内置一个专门的密码应用程序不仅会让这一切变得更容易，而且还给人们多一个留在苹果生态系统中的理由。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>据报道，就像它的竞争对手一样，苹果的密码应用程序将把密码分为不同的类别，如帐户、WiFi 网络和密码（这是我们<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/passkeys-passwords-authentication-security-133024414.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/passkeys-passwords-authentication-security-133024414.html">深入</a>解释它们如何工作的）。它还允许您从竞争对手的应用程序导入密码，并在您的设备检测到您正在登录网站或应用程序时自动填写密码。密码也适用于苹果售价 4,000 美元的<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-review-beta-testing-the-future-201430272.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-review-beta-testing-the-future-201430272.html">Vision Pro</a>耳机，并且与 Google Authenticator 和 Authy 一样，将支持双因素验证码。目前尚不清楚的是，除了密码之外，密码应用程序是否还能让您安全地存储文件和图像，这是 1Password 和 LastPass 都<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-password-manager-134639599.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/best-password-manager-134639599.html">提供的</a>。</p><p>除了密码之外，苹果<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/wwdc-2024-what-we-expect-to-come-out-of-apples-keynote-and-how-to-watch-195802167.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/wwdc-2024-what-we-expect-to-come-out-of-apples-keynote-and-how-to-watch-195802167.html">预计</a>还将在周一发布 iOS、iPadOS、MacOS、WatchOS 和 VisionOS 的下一个版本。据报道，该软件的新版本将注入全新的人工智能功能。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f6d99065-6d34-4c64-92fd-549656e71e04 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Pranav Dixit]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 06 Jun 2024 21:18:12 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1717708693</ingested><modified> 2024-06-06T21:18:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><cat